data.description: Come check out this beautiful home in the highly sought after Parish Crossing community! This 3-bed, 2-bath home sits on a 0.51-acre lot and has all the space you need. As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by the gas fireplace in the living room. This is the ultimate resting venue to wind down after a long day of work. The spacious owner's suite offers vault ceilings, walk-in closet and the owner's bathroom has double vanities and jacuzzi with separate shower. The kitchen has upgraded shaker kitchen cabinets and quartz countertops. The home offers LVP throughout the main living areas and bathrooms. The backyard is fully fenced to create a privacy haven. Additionally, the backyard offers a massive and versatile space to either throw cookouts to entertain guests and loved ones, or, simply relax by the fire pit on a quite and relaxing evening. This home is only minutes from Fort Stewart.
